<br>
If God has the power to prevent horrible deaths of infants or children, and yet <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>doesn't</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> prevent those horrible deaths, what does that say about God? Alternately, what if God doesn't have the power to prevent said horrible deaths?<br>
